        "body": "Task: json-average-calculator\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\nReads JSON from /app/input.txt, computes average scores (rounded to 2 decimals),\r\nand writes output to /app/output.txt.\r\n\r\nValidation Results:\r\n\r\nOracle:\r\nuv run harbor run --agent oracle --path harbor_tasks/json-average-calculator --job-name test-oracle\r\nScore: 1.0\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1600\" height=\"1005\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/dfd40bd3-8ffd-4ef1-8ce5-a0879841dc74\" />\r\n\r\nNOP:\r\nuv run harbor run --agent nop --path harbor_tasks/json-average-calculator --job-name test-nop\r\nScore: 0.0\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1600\" height=\"1016\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c1c5e720-deab-4245-8368-df17351b477e\" />\r\n\r\nRuff:\r\nuvx ruff check harbor_tasks/json-average-calculator\r\nAll checks passed.\n<!-- devin-review-badge-begin -->\n\n---\n\n<a href=\"https://app.devin.ai/review/laude-institute/harbor/pull/901\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-dark.svg?v=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-light.svg?v=1\" alt=\"Open with Devin\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<!-- devin-review-badge-end -->\n",
