        "body": "## Description\r\nEnhances the string utility functions in `@shikijs/core` with improved edge case handling and more robust language detection.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n- Add empty string handling to `splitLines()`\r\n- Enhance `guessEmbeddedLanguages()` to detect:\r\n  - Script type attributes (`type=\"text/javascript\"`)\r\n  - MIME types (application/typescript, text/javascript)\r\n  - Vue v-bind syntax (`:lang=\"...\"`)\r\n  - Normalize case and handle whitespace\r\n- Add 17 comprehensive test cases with 100% pass rate\r\n\r\n## Testing\r\nAll 63 tests pass including 17 new tests covering edge cases and new functionality.\r\n\r\nImproves robustness when processing various code formats, particularly Vue SFC and Markdown files with embedded code blocks.",
